message.body: Cooper looks like he is getting so big. You may need to exchange clothes for a bigger size.

Good. I leave this wed for San Diego am anxious to see Linds and her home. We will drive by the house we rented for this summer while I am there. It is actually on Encinitas about 30min north of the airport. How did you like Lindsay's house and the area she lives in?

A lot of really cool restaurants around. A few nice wine bars too...
